# SU 14 — Trophy / Endgame

<div class="legos-card">
LEGOS atoms:

locations: `loc_living`, `loc_stone_barrow`  
entities: `ent_case`, all treasures  
goals: `g_case`, `g_master`  
shifts: `sh_win`
</div>

<div class="past">PAST: the trophy case has waited as an empty grammar for recovered empire objects.</div>

<div class="present">PRESENT: each treasure is deposited; the house becomes a ledger of solved transformations.</div>

<div class="future">FUTURE: the final treasure produces a map to the Stone Barrow; completion opens the next game.</div>

ABC seed: the opening room returns transformed; the ordinary case becomes a portal because every object now carries a solved past.

